<p>Precinct files supplied to <a href="https://populardemocracy.org">Popular Democracy</a>, <a href="https://movementcooperative.org">The Movement Cooperative</a>, and the <a href="https://workingfamilies.org">Working Families Party</a>; precincts donated to Hillary Clinton's 2016 run.</p>
