  <!-- ============ FEATURE: GEORGIA RUNOFFS ============ -->
  <item>
    <title><![CDATA[Georgia runoffs]]></title>
    <link>https://siegeanalytics.com/work/georgia-runoffs/</link>
    <dc:creator><![CDATA[dheeraj]]></dc:creator>
    <guid isPermaLink="false">https://siegeanalytics.com/?page_id=111</guid>
    <content:encoded><![CDATA[
<p class="eyebrow">Case study · 2024</p>
<h1>Where-first targeting in the Georgia runoffs.</h1>
<p class="lede">Re-deriving location from the address itself surfaced tens of thousands of contactable voters a list-first program would have missed. Successful contact rose 23 points.</p>
<p>We graded every geocode, re-joined the file to current district boundaries, and clustered the result into micro-turf. The incremental universe concentrated in three exurban precincts that decided the margin.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
